name: SOLUTEC TCHAD
product_desc:
SOLUTEC TCHAD is a multi-disciplinary firm, created in 2014, which aims to provide Chadian companies with state-of-the-art technological support in order to bring them to the level of global competition in the fields of 'engineering.
SOLUTEC TCHAD offers solutions tailored to the needs of medium-sized companies, craftsmen, tradesmen, liberal professions, hotels, schools and universities and individuals.
Supplier of all engineering applications, SOLUTEC TCHAD provides the following services:  Information and Communication Technologies, industrial engineering,  civil engineering and training
